Output docs/demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1240
Set Height 520
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 24
Set Framerate 24
Set TypingSpeed 42ms

Type "# Paste a store link or extension ID"
Sleep 350ms
Enter 2

Type "npx crxray pifapfmbofjgaenkhhipjhfacfmmhkcp"
Sleep 300ms
Enter

Hide
Type "bash docs/record-demo-play.sh"
Enter
Sleep 6s
Show
Sleep 2s
